{"tid":1575781,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"<831> 列車於8:30至8:32間出軌  3人送醫院","createTime":"2019-09-17T03:22:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T04:53:00.000Z","uid":227801,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"3f041cfba14adb32f130b52a10383ddf8e6fa426","tid":1575781,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T03:22:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190917/mobile/bkn-20190917084004132-0917_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190917%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190917084004132-0917_00822_001.html&d=CoEtBkFB9dbfLkjoGL86rUYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=84cb24cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190917/mobile/bkn-20190917084004132-0917_00822_001.html</a><br />\n港鐵發生嚴重事故，今早(17日)8時30分，東鐵線一架駛往紅磡站方向的列車，駛至紅磡站前數十米，突然出軌。據悉，列車損毀斷開兩截，多名乘客受傷。受影響乘客落車徒步離開，返回車站。多輛消防車及救護車輛到場救援。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190917/60052798\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190917%2F60052798&d=CoEtBkFB9dbfLkjoGL86rUYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=f11d9ca8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190917%2F60052798&h=7c25d4c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190917/60052798</a><br />\n上午8時32分，港鐵東鐵綫有列車在紅磡站出軌。現場所見，車內有乘客數十人，全部落車，正沿路軌行入紅磡站。列車最少分為兩截，車卡之間明顯損毀，同時有車門甩脫。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1480994-20190917.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1480994-20190917.htm&d=CoEtBkFB9dbfLkjoGL86rUYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=ff1961e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1480994-20190917.htm&h=ba970937\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1480994-20190917.htm</a><br />\n東鐵綫紅磡站附近有列車出軌，3人需要送往伊利沙伯醫院，送院時清醒。"},{"pid":"81813b948bbe68353c0a0a1e87d8aa6e10298eb5","tid":1575781,"uid":269515,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T03:22:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KfD0tDh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKfD0tDh.png&h=ec697e2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x8RhvRC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx8RhvRC.png&h=96d9c538&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e3e6fde7e5d3f48b1e685b91d157d31aef7d11ca","tid":1575781,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T03:23:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TrPZKfU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrPZKfU.jpg&h=433e1fe6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"53b6a1c9f43bbee031b6a347e5c7c5a449c851ea","tid":1575781,"uid":52609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T03:23:51.000Z","msg":"831<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4d59d39198684474391c88dd3594297fdb1e8a4","tid":1575781,"uid":67023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T03:24:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f94e0eb2625ec42a85c53b780d1980e0201780b","tid":1575781,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T03:27:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\